Tanzanian star Diamond Platnumz has alleged that his ex wife Zari Hassan cheated severally on him and this was why the relationship went over the hills. While on a radio show, Diamond alleged that not only did Zari have an affair with her personal trainer, she also slept with Peter Okoye of the defunct PSquare group. He reiterates that although he loved her despite everything, it was saddening. He added that he confronted Peter Okoye with a text message. 